videos.description: Satou Sabally can't find anyone to inbound the ball to, so she banks it off Jordan Danberry's backside to keep possession for the Ducks.
videos.headline: Sabally inbounds ball off defender to escape trouble

videos.description: Chloe Bibby is off the mark on her jumper, but Teaira McCowan collects the miss and finishes while falling to the floor for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: McCowan battles for and-1 putback

videos.description: Anriel Howard makes a beautiful move to finish inside, then Jordan Danberry gets the steal and finds Chloe Bibby, who ties the game at 24-24.
videos.headline: Bulldogs score, steal, score again to tie game

videos.description: Oti Gildon's inbounds pass nearly gets stolen, but the deflection goes right to Sabrina Ionescu, who finds Maite Cazorla for the crucial fast-break bucket.
videos.headline: Lucky bounce gives Oregon dagger fast-break layup
